    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081830/extras/4f31813ff729359a7c9cb7192b7876b6.poster.avif?t=1769301913\" width=640 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081830/extras/4f31813ff729359a7c9cb7192b7876b6.webm?t=1769301913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081830/extras/4f31813ff729359a7c9cb7192b7876b6.mp4?t=1769301913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil forces have emerged, spreading chaos across the land. Shiraken members went to investigate, but they haven't returned! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Shiranui Flare in this retro action platformer, wielding her dual pistols Smile and Go (names subject to change), as you explore the world on a quest to save your friends!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Quest</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A vast lineup of Hololive members to meet, some will lend you their strength while others will challenge you as fierce bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels filled with power-ups, items and secrets </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A soundtrack featuring a collection of 8-bit versions of Hololive songs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A range of challenging achievements for players eager to test their skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Numerous checkpoints and helpful Elfriends for players seeking a more relaxed experience</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But Wait, There's More!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two additional quests await you! Play as Usada Pekora and Houshou Marine in their unique campaigns to uncover different aspects of the story and experience new gameplay styles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>If your controller doesn't respond, please try to “Disable Steam Input”.</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081830/extras/86d43bbef5214083bb3541a1974b42b4.apng?t=1769301913\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081830/extras/86d43bbef5214083bb3541a1974b42b4.poster.avif?t=1769301913\" class=\"bb_img\" width=144 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is published under CCMC Corp(※1)'s Indie game brand &quot;holo Indie&quot;.(※2)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is allowed to be monetized under the examination and terms of &quot;holo Indie&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that any monetized derivative work games that include Cover Corp.'s content outside of holo Indie is not covered by these terms and is not allowed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※1. About CCMC Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CCMC Corp. is entrusted with website management (ex: steam) including, examination, publishing and other necessary tasks by Cover Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※2. About &quot;holo Indie&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >holo Indie's objective is to cooperate with hololive production fans and creators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a game brand that offers &quot;Game Creator Support Program&quot; for the derivative work games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For more details about &quot;holo Indie&quot;, Please refer to the Cover Corp.'s &quot;Derivative work guidelines&quot;.</p>",
